  "2026-07-12T21:01:05.591Z",codex-frontmatter-vocabulary,"Evidence: pm-cli PR #531 Gates (static) failed because published pm-changelog imported removed listAllFrontMatter. Updated source and built extension artifacts to listAllItemMetadata and item metadata wording; installed the local pm-cli PR package without saving dependency changes; npm build passed and all 108 tests passed, including package install/activation coverage."
